I know why only moved pointer dispatches on iOS but not on Android. https://github.com/flutter/engine/blob/main/shell/platform/darwin/ios/framework/Source/FlutterViewController.mm#:~:text=%2D%20(void)dispatchTouches,(UIEvent*)event%20%7B  In the dispatchTouches function, it should use the event.alltouches.

